fields.name: Hex Bar - 20kg
fields.description:
Made of durable, heavy-duty solid chrome steel with a weight capacity of 300KG. This Hex Olympic barbell lifting bar has rotating sleeves with brass bushings for a smooth 360° spin during training.
The handles feature a knurled grip design and are made from chrome steel to provide a greater level of grip which improves control during heavy deadlifts, shrugs and farmers walks.
IWF Standards - The Hex Olympic barbell bar is compatible with 2 inch weight plates and designed for maximum weight loading capacity allowing continuous powerlifting and bodybuilding progression.

fields.name: PhysKcal EZ Curl Bar - 9.5kg
fields.description:
The PhsyKcal Curl Bars are made with high-quality steel and hold up to 367kg/810lbs. This ez curl bar is designed to challenge your limits and hold heavy weights for curls, rows, extensions, zercher squats, and more!
This Curl Bar has a length of 120CM which makes it a perfect workout equipment for gyms with a smaller space or during a fitness class with many participants.

fields.name: PhysKcal Tri-Grip Weight Plate - 20kg
fields.description: These weight plates are made of perfectly-balanced solid cast iron with impeccable craftsmanship. The 5-mm dense and durable rubber finish not only reduces excessive noise and floor damages but also resistant to corrosion. The flange-around centre ring made of stainless steel reduces abrasion to the bar sleeves, thus prolonging the life of your barbells and plates.

fields.name: MuscleSquad 32.5kg Adjustable Dumbbell - 12 in 1 Dumbbell - 5kg to 32.5kg
fields.description:
This dumbbell, built with adjustable weights, allows you to customize your workout in seconds. Our heavy-duty, chrome-plated steel dumbbell set features a simple and elegant design, whilst providing you with an excellent all-round workout experience. Note that when you buy this option it is a PAIR OF DUMBBELLS.

Our adjustable dumbbell set goes from 5kg (5.5lb) to 32.5kg (71.5lbs) in 2.5kg increments with a turn of the dial. You’ll get 5kg, 7.5kg, 10kg, 12.5kg, 15kg, 17.5kg, 20kg, 22.5kg, 25kg, 27.5kg, 30kg and 32.5kg weights in one dumbbell. Simply select, twist and lift!

fields.name: Rockbase Bumper Weight Plate - 5kg
fields.description:
HEAVY DUTY WEIGHT PLATES FOR LONG LASTING DURABILITY - Built with a solid cast iron metal core encased in a heavy-duty rubber coating, the Olympic weight plates have been expertly designed for high level performance to withstand highly repetitive usage for even the most hardened of weightlifting enthusiasts.
Unlike standard cast iron weights discs, our vinyl weight plates enables users to perform a range of compound and isolated movements, improving stability and control as well as overall strength and fitness.
The rubber Olympic weight plates are specifically designed to prevent flooring from impact damage caused by plate dropping. The rubber finish also helps to reduce impact noise for a quieter, less obstructive workout in your home gym space.
